value.0: Fashioned from rough iron, these bars extend into a narrow slot in the floor.
The stout planks of this bench have been worn smooth by years of use.
Allows the user to create a town portal leading back to town. When the creator enters the portal, it will be destroyed immediately after use. Thus it's adviced to let your party members enter first.
